{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "15", "m": "03", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "14", "M": "19", "S": "45"}}, "news": [{"title": "Jammu & Kashmir achieves 97% target under PMAY-G, 3.23 lakh houses built", "para": "Jammu and Kashmir has successfully completed over 3 lakh houses under Pradhan Mantri Awas Yojana-Gramin, achieving 97% of its target. Officials are now urged to expedite work on the remaining 11,340 houses, with a strict deadline of April 15 for all pending constructions before the new phase commences.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/jammu-kashmir-surpasses-housing-goals-323-lakh-houses-built-under-pmay-g/129590228?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-22982/129590228.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "Goa: Consumer forum tells developer to repair seepage in flat", "para": "A property developer has been ordered by the North Goa District Consumer Dispute Redressal Commission to repair water seepage in a flat within three months. The developer must also pay Rs 25,000 for damages caused by leakage. The commission found the builder responsible for addressing structural cracks and defective waterproofing.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/goa-consumer-forum-orders-developer-to-fix-water-leakage-in-flat-and-compensate-resident/129590844?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-33766/129590844.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}, {"title": "Uttar Pradesh stamps department opens campaign to boost revenue collection", "para": "The Stamp and Registration Department is actively working to increase revenue before the financial year ends. They are prioritizing the registration of unregistered properties from various authorities and institutions. This initiative aims to collect significant revenue through timely stamp duty payments on ongoing projects.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/regulatory/uttar-pradesh-launches-major-campaign-to-increase-stamp-revenue/129590823?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-42916/129590823.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "regulatory"}]}